beer.beer_description:
A mid-strength IPA that has followed in the footsteps of our original IPA, Bling and its big brother the imperial IPA, Bling Bling.

This beer offers craft beer lovers a mid-strength alternative that doesn’t compromise on flavour.

Just like it siblings this beer is also about balance between hop and malt flavour.
